<html>
  <head>
    <title>Welcome to Vanlog-express</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;
      background-color: #f9f9f9; margin: 0; padding: 0; } .container {
      max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; background: #ffffff; padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); } h1 {
      color: #4CAF50; } .button { display: inline-block; margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 16px; color: #ffffff; background-color:
      #4CAF50; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; } .button:hover {
      background-color: #45a049; } footer { margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px;
      color: #777; text-align: center; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <h1>Welcome, {{companyName}}!</h1>
      <p>We are excited to let you know that your account has been approved by
        the admin team. You can now log in and start exploring our platform!</p>
      <p>To log in, click the button below:</p>
      <a class='button' href='{{loginUrl}}'>Log In</a>
      <p>Or from this direct link:</p>
      <a href='{{loginUrl}}'>Log In</a>
      <p>If you have any questions or encounter any issues, feel free to contact
        our support team.</p>
      <p>Thank you for joining us!</p>
      <p>Best regards,</p>
      <p>Vanlog-express</p>
      <footer>
        <p>&copy; {{year}} Vanlog-express. All rights reserved.</p>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>